window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>One great series in a single offering!</p> <p>Keep my Promises, Wed the Princess, Prevent a Catastrophe!</p> <p>Imagine my luck when I'm transported to a fantasy world where magic is real, beautiful women are bountiful, and the Blessing of a Goddess creates endless opportunities. Yeah, it is one hell of a way to arrive. Unfortunately, I've got some work to do because my heroic actions just triggered the End of an Age. With the help of some lovely new allies, we might just save the day or die trying.</p>"; 
